    "Id": "chassisdef_texihuitl_TEX-R2",
    "Name": "Texihuitl",
    "Details": "The -R2 is even more extreme in its focus than the -R1, the variant drops most of the cutting edge experimental technology but instead manages to fit two Heavy MRM-60 launchers. Thanks to its 19 compact heat sinks the 'Mech can somewhat manage the immense heat buildup of the huge launchers, relaying on its Emergency Coolant System to not overheat in repeated volley situations. A total of 8 tons of varied ammunition types means the R2 is able to fire more salvos than the earlier R1 design.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - HMRM</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.43</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
